      • _parseHtml

        protected Categories _parseHtml(HCardElement element,
                                ParseContext context)
        Description copied from class: VCardPropertyScribe

        Unmarshals the property from an hCard (HTML document).

        This method should be overridden by child classes that wish to support hCard. The default implementation of this method will retrieve the HTML element's hCard value (as described in HCardElement.value()), and pass it into the VCardPropertyScribe._parseText(java.lang.String, ezvcard.VCardDataType, ezvcard.parameter.VCardParameters, ezvcard.io.ParseContext) method.

        Overrides:
        _parseHtml in class VCardPropertyScribe<Categories>
        Parameters:
        element - the property's HTML element
        context - the parse context
        Returns:
        the unmarshalled property object
